Exploring a container:

1. Launch and start the container.
2. Do docker exec -it [container name] sh

To log into MariaDB:

- as a specified user:
    docker exec -it [mariadb] mysql -u [username] -p
- as root:
    docker exec -it [mariadb] mysql -u root -p

To check databases:

1. SHOW DATABASES;
2. USE [database name] #wordpress
3. SHOW TABLES;
4. SELECT * FROM [table_name];